7:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理性分析：<br />\n假設我就7-11買嘢，比錢個震又要開個App，又要等個收銀員Scan個QR Code。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解我唔直接拎張八達通嘟一嘟， 咁樣會唔會方便啲呢。</blockquote><br />\n信用卡都咇完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5592cbad42588d5eb8ee7fa2be4138389096a762","tid":447852,"uid":42764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T18:10:17.000Z","msg":"下下開相機，個mon又光，手機好快無電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d848396c5ae2ab0dceb5a99b3c3683ff145d9a","tid":447852,"uid":103497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先唔講QR CODE的安全問題係唔係真係咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQr code只係一個communication channel,支付寶完全可以聽日出一個NFC 功能，特別係ios11已經有api</blockquote><br />\n出到先講啦垃圾科技當寶物"},{"pid":"e3f6ce8b9fc348be25a30e565bd5afa220fa45a0","tid":447852,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先唔講QR CODE的安全問題係唔係真係咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQr code只係一個communication channel,支付寶完全可以聽日出一個NFC 功能，特別係ios11已經有api</blockquote><br />\n出到先講啦垃圾科技當寶物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNFC 功能唔係部部手機都有，且比較晒電。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，手機支付點都比信用卡安全。呢點好重要。<br />\n<br />\n信用卡，你NUMBER 和驗證碼都print晒出黎。又可以透支，安全系數最低。但交易額又好高。"},{"pid":"101b66cbab19745f9ff3b24f09d9c0717990434c","tid":447852,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先唔講QR CODE的安全問題係唔係真係咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQr code只係一個communication channel,支付寶完全可以聽日出一個NFC 功能，特別係ios11已經有api</blockquote><br />\n出到先講啦垃圾科技當寶物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出唔係難，技術上好易做。<br />\n<br />\n只係用戶習慣上，同埋用戶手機唔係部部都support到。"},{"pid":"ceef0b93a954f4e855c479f5e14e5a12237409d2","tid":447852,"uid":686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先唔講QR CODE的安全問題係唔係真係咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQr code只係一個communication channel,支付寶完全可以聽日出一個NFC 功能，特別係ios11已經有api</blockquote><br />\n出到先講啦垃圾科技當寶物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNFC 功能唔係部部手機都有，且比較晒電。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，手機支付點都比信用卡安全。呢點好重要。<br />\n<br />\n信用卡，你NUMBER 和驗證碼都print晒出黎。又可以透支，安全系數最低。但交易額又好高。</blockquote><br />\n所以咪有Apple Pay, Android Pay, Samsung Pay囉"},{"pid":"6242bcc534350aca6bc510329e897ce62b98b121","tid":447852,"uid":20227,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8d39f2f9d53a62b1b6b75f9c1cb799f6efd708f","tid":447852,"uid":2446,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"支那人窮 唔係個個有NFC 所以咪折衷用呢種低級技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開相機黎搞 人地近場形式要唔要連線嘅交易形式都交易完成 支那寶隨時仲開緊相機/app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a73355b3424595b51049b307f3b085b33eabc4","tid":447852,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"最重要既野 你先唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e104c7dae225d215764548f4e0fd4e56043ac8d8","tid":447852,"uid":62085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"好似為電子化而電子化咁"},{"pid":"1c453bc55815e47ae87f273c63b951b81b452647","tid":447852,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"Iphone有冇開放nfc? 又咪淨係收埋用係apple pay<br />\n用nfc即係放棄一半市場？"},{"pid":"a0858705f77d5e45100dd4849a15a05f07530e65","tid":447852,"uid":51399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"八達通都話想用qr code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif